column5: Where can I buy a pound of leeches in late June in Kenora? Phone number or address would help. Thanks

John,The best place for bait in Kenora is Sunset Bait 1407 HWY 17E 807-468-9567 On Highway 17 East end of Kenora.E-mail me after you get back from your trip.Will be leaving on June 8th to Gold Arrow Resort by Perrault Falls on Red Lake roadLarry S
